Grand Designs Australia - Season 4, Episode 2




South Melbourne Brick House

As a brick-layer, Greg Saunders has spent most of his adult life building houses for other people. Now after dreaming about it for more than twenty years, he's doing it for himself out of the materials he's most passionate about -- bricks.




Original Air Date: 17-Oct-2013
